default1.6.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIf our academy chain provides a “snapshot” of education, it shows  starkly the task that needs to be carried out nationally. It begs the question about what Local Authorities (LAs) have been doing in the area of school improvement over the last couple of decades, as we are having to change totally the ethos and culture in most of our 
