defaulthool. However, a regionally elected board, comprising of successful academy headteachers, with a DfE appointed chairman could be the body with powers of intervention and support as the system gradually moves to a self-regulatory system.
default The logic sho
defaultuld be as academies improve and standards rise  less intervention should be required. 
