default&#xa0;default4.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAll academies are accountable to their local community and the local community elect the local councillors.  Therefore all academies should be held to account by the local authority for the progress of the academy.  Essex has produced a “Memorandum of Understanding” which encompasses this accountability.  TKAT openly shares its data with local authorities and where we have a good relationship with the LA then the 
defaultLA supplies us with information they hold centrally on the schools
default.  Other LAs 
defaultare not so forthcoming.
